{"tid":1586182,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"勸大家唔好設咁多底線俾自己","createTime":"2019-09-21T22:15:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T02:07:33.000Z","uid":203867,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fefe1d14f5442ffdbf28217f096f129959fcb080","tid":1586182,"uid":203867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T22:15:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">因為呢個仆街政權根本係無底線咁打壓我地!</span><br />\n<br />\n點解到今日仲聽到輸民意?!香港仲有大撚把人覺得示威無問題但係咪撚阻住我揾錢，係咪要等到呢班人醒埋先可以升級呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港無時間再拖落去喇各位!依家係任何俾到壓力呢個仆街政權嘅野都要做呀屌!係呀係暴力㗎喇，但係唔好忘記對面比我地更暴力!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n贏咗就係革命 輸咗就係暴動 食粥食飯自己揀<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"c1022befc23c11ee20907246d8ed53b7afbe913f","tid":1586182,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T22:15:49.000Z","msg":"有人話過抗爭係冇底線<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a254196cced3d26368cb7f09da5991123a49288","tid":1586182,"uid":53361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T22:17:57.000Z","msg":"同班左膠講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地聽得入耳咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edcb925f45263865af04a1d868813e8202762a92","tid":1586182,"uid":78304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6a254196cced3d26368cb7f09da5991123a49288","tid":1586182,"uid":53361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T22:17:57.000Z","msg":"同班左膠講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地聽得入耳咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T22:22:46.000Z","msg":"感化左膠做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2014 咩<br />\n左膠同藍蛆，支蝗一樣都係敵人"},{"pid":"f5d2cc7c1958acdce5cd3f9